### Features

 - Quick HTML form’s element creation.
 - Ability to save and restore previous submitted form data.

### Example

Create HTML `<input type="text">` element:

~~~ .php
echo Form::text();
~~~

Store previous form data on error:

~~~ .php
if (Message::$x) {
    Session::set(Form::session, HTTP::post());
}
~~~

